      <title>中国黑客攻击菲律宾总统，窃取军事数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/chinese-hackers-target-philippine-president-steal-military-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位知情人士透露，在长达一年的行动中，受中国政府支持的黑客已经侵入菲律宾政府行政部门并窃取了敏感数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/chinese-hackers-target-philippine-president-steal-military-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国前大亨郭文贵的幕僚长因诈骗 10 亿美元被判入狱 10 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-06/self-exiled-chinese-businessman-s-chief-of-staff-gets-10-years-in-prison-in-1b-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——中国政府通缉的一名中国商人的幕僚长因参与 10 亿美元欺诈案于周一被判处 10 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-06/self-exiled-chinese-businessman-s-chief-of-staff-gets-10-years-in-prison-in-1b-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 23:58:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡与马来西亚将达成协议建立大型经济区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/singapore-malaysia-to-finalize-deal-creating-vast-economic-zone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚和新加坡领导人即将正式签署一项协议，建立连接两国边境地区的经济特区，但直接经济利益的前景可能取决于这项自 2023 年谈判开始以来一再被推迟的协议的实施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/singapore-malaysia-to-finalize-deal-creating-vast-economic-zone</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省希望通过保证石油产量来刺激新管道建设</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/alberta-looks-to-spur-new-pipelines-by-guaranteeing-barrels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省政府计划直接向新管道项目投入石油，以加速加拿大西部省份的石油生产扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/alberta-looks-to-spur-new-pipelines-by-guaranteeing-barrels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 21:39:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在使用关税工具时保留多种选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-06/trump-s-keeps-his-options-open-in-wielding-the-tariff-tool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，有关首都的金钱、权力和政治的新闻通讯。今天，经济治国记者 Daniel Flatley 关注唐纳德·特朗普如何使用他最喜欢的工具：关税威胁。在此注册并关注我们 @bpolitics。在此向我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-06/trump-s-keeps-his-options-open-in-wielding-the-tariff-tool</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 21:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普小特朗普计划惊喜访问格陵兰岛 因美国购买格陵兰岛传闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-jr-plans-surprise-greenland-visit-amid-independence-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小唐纳德·特朗普本周将前往格陵兰岛，对这片北极领土进行意外访问。几周前，他的父亲、美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普重新燃起从丹麦手中购买该岛的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-jr-plans-surprise-greenland-visit-amid-independence-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 20:48:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼、弗里兰和内阁部长均有望接替特鲁多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/carney-freeland-lead-list-of-contenders-to-succeed-trudeau-as-canada-s-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多周一表示，他将在未来几个月卸任加拿大总理一职，结束他连续三次赢得选举和九年担任加拿大最高政治职务的政治生涯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/carney-freeland-lead-list-of-contenders-to-succeed-trudeau-as-canada-s-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 19:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多执政九年后辞职，自由党迫使他下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trudeau-resigns-after-nine-years-in-power-as-liberals-force-him-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多担任加拿大总理九年多后，因糟糕的民意调查和其所执政的自由党内部的叛乱而辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trudeau-resigns-after-nine-years-in-power-as-liberals-force-him-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 16:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官拒绝延期，特朗普将于 1 月 10 日宣判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-asks-new-york-appeals-court-to-stop-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普未能说服纽约一名法官推迟对其封口费刑事案件的宣判，除非上诉法院介入，否则相关听证会仍将于 1 月 10 日举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-asks-new-york-appeals-court-to-stop-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉挑战者会见拜登，向特朗普施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/venezuela-challenger-to-meet-biden-putting-pressure-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普入主华盛顿的几天前，这位被美国承认为当选总统的委内瑞拉反对派领导人与总统乔·拜登会面，并面临着如何处理与这个无证移民主要来源国的关系的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/venezuela-challenger-to-meet-biden-putting-pressure-on-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
